# AddressSanitizer suppressions for VTX.
#
# Format: one pattern per line.  Lines starting with # are comments.
#
#   interceptor_via_fun:<substring of function>
#   interceptor_via_lib:<substring of library name>
#
# Example (uncomment when needed):
#   # Known leak in libprotobuf's global init, deliberate design.
#   # leak:google::protobuf::internal::OnShutdown
